snippet.title: Top 20 TV Shows Turning 20 This Year
snippet.description:
Can you believe these shows are turning 20? Join us as we count down the most iconic TV series that premiered in 2006! From serial killers to small-town football, workplace comedies to supernatural adventures, this year introduced us to some unforgettable characters and stories that still influence television today. Our countdown includes "Dexter," "30 Rock," "Heroes," "Psych," "Hannah Montana," "Ugly Betty," "The IT Crowd," "Torchwood," and more! These shows captured the mid-2000s zeitgeist perfectly, from the rise of the TV antihero to network rebrands and the early days of cult fandom on the internet. Which of these nostalgic favorites defined your viewing experience back then? Tell us in the comments!
